<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #1f4632; padding: 2rem;">
  <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">Hi <%= @subscription.user.first_name %>,</p>

  <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
    Welcome to <strong>gooi</strong>. We're excited to have you on board and thrilled that you're joining us in reducing waste and building a cleaner planet.
  </p>

  <% if @subscription.once_off? %>

    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
      Your once-off collection invoice has been generated. Please settle it to confirm your booking — Alfred will collect your organic waste on
      <strong><%= @subscription.start_date&.strftime("%A, %-d %B") || @subscription.collection_day %></strong>.
    </p>

    <p style="margin: 1.5rem 0;">
      <a href="<%= invoice_url(@subscription.invoices.order(created_at: :asc).first) %>"
         style="background-color: #FBB718; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 40px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">
        View & Pay Invoice
      </a>
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
      Have your organic waste ready in a bag or bucket before Alfred arrives. If you want to coordinate the details,
      <a href="https://wa.me/27785325513" style="color: #1f4632; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">message Alfred on WhatsApp</a>.
    </p>

  <% else %>

    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
      Your <strong>starter kit invoice</strong> has been generated. It includes your compost bin, compostable bags, and a helpful guide to get you going.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
      To get everything delivered on time, please settle your invoice using SnapScan or EFT:
    </p>

    <p style="margin: 1.5rem 0;">
      <a href="<%= invoice_url(@subscription.invoices.order(created_at: :asc).first) %>"
         style="background-color: #FBB718; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 40px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">
        View & Pay Invoice
      </a>
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
      We'll be in your neighbourhood on <strong><%= @subscription.collection_day %></strong>. Your starter kit will arrive in week one, and from then on, just have your full bag ready for collection.
    </p>

  <% end %>

  <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
    If you need a reminder or want to revisit the onboarding details, you can always return to your <a href="<%= welcome_subscription_url(@subscription) %>" style="color: #1f4632; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">welcome page</a>.
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
    Thanks again for joining — we're so happy to have you with us!
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">Warm regards,</p>

  <p>
    <%= image_tag 'email-signature.png', alt: "Kristen Kennedy email signature", style: "max-width: 250px; margin-top: 10px;" %>
  </p>
</div>
